Package ui.input.selection

Class UnselectableSection<T extends Section>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ui.drawing.DrawableSection
      • ui.input.selection.UnselectableSection<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of underlying section to store.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    PrintHandler, Section, SelectableSection, SelectionHandler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UnselectableBufferedSection, UnselectableResponsiveSection
    public class UnselectableSection<T extends Section>
extends DrawableSection
implements SelectableSection
    Allows an unselectable section to be used like a selectable one. Implements the SelectableSection interface with dummy values.
    Represents a section that can be drawn to the terminal window.
